# CraftSpace Frontend Detailed Specification

## 1. Overview

The frontend is implemented using **React 18+** with **JavaScript (or optionally TypeScript)**, styled with **Tailwind CSS v3+**. It communicates with the backend REST APIs over HTTPS and handles JWT authentication locally in secure storage.

---

## 2. Technology Stack and Versions

- React 18.x
- JavaScript (ES2021+) or optionally TypeScript 4.x
- Tailwind CSS v3.x for utility-first styling
- React Router v6 for client-side routing
- Axios v1.x for HTTP requests
- JWT-decode for decoding and managing JWT tokens (optional)
- React Query (TanStack Query) v4.x for API data fetching and caching (optional but recommended)
- ESLint + Prettier for code quality and formatting
- Vite or Create React App for project bootstrapping (Vite preferred for modern dev experience)
- React Hook Form v7.x for form handling and validation (optional but recommended)
- Heroicons or similar SVG icon library (optional)

